        "segment": [
            {
                "text": "Two weeks into Operation Epic Fury, the military campaign to dismantle Iran's ballistic and nuclear capabilities has triggered a global crisis.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 7.68
            },
            {
                "text": "While the initial air assault targeted air defenses and naval assets, the Iranian regime remains in power and is lashing out.",
                "start": 7.92,
                "end": 14.48
            },
            {
                "text": "The conflict has rapidly escalated across the Middle East with Iranian missiles striking Israel and American bases.",
                "start": 14.64,
                "end": 20.400000000000002
            },
            {
                "text": "Beyond the immediate combat zones, the humanitarian toll is staggering.",
                "start": 20.64,
                "end": 25.12
            },
            {
                "text": "The United Nations reports that over 3 million people are now displaced as civilians flee major cities.",
                "start": 25.36,
                "end": 30.88
            },
            {
                "text": "Economically, the world is reeling as the Strait of Hormuz remains effectively choked off, disrupting 20% of the global oil supply.",
                "start": 31.12,
                "end": 38.480000000000004
            },
            {
                "text": "In response to surging costs, European governments are moving to crack down on price gouging by energy firms.",
                "start": 38.72,
                "end": 44.56
            },
            {
                "text": "This escalation has left Washington's Gulf allies in a state of profound shock as regional stability evaporates.",
                "start": 44.72,
                "end": 51.52
            },
            {
                "text": "Despite U.S.",
                "start": 51.76,
                "end": 52.64
            },
            {
                "text": "efforts to pivot away from the Middle East, this conflict proves the region continues to dominate American foreign policy.",
                "start": 52.72,
                "end": 58.480000000000004
            }
        ]
    },
